comments.text:
Insym is guilty of not paying attention to things in this video; the sort of stuff he'd chide CJ and Psycho for in other videos.  
The game's stock purchase terminal tells you how many of a product you have in the store, yet he just spam purchases stuff.  Then he doesn't finish the older stock first; violating the old store adage of FIFO(first in, first out).  But to be fair I suppose if he didn't spam purchase CJ would just spam decorations with the money instead...
